parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Tread Separation and Blowout of Firestone SteelTex Tires
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden tread separation and blowout of Firestone SteelTex tires can cause loss of control, accidents, and damage to the vehicle, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Tread peeling off
tire blowout
loss of air pressure
blue smoke coming from the rear of the vehicle
pieces of rubber flying everywhere
and damage to the vehicle's underside or storage compartments.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rust corrosion under the coach can lead to structural weakening, potentially causing accidents or injuries. Specifically, if the rust reaches the propane tanks, it can cause a leak, which may result in an explosion, posing a significant threat to vehicle occupants and bystanders.
symptoms: Visible rust or corrosion under the coach
especially around the propane tanks
rusty water or debris accumulation under the coach
strange noises or vibrations while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Corrosion of the propane tanks can cause a leak, leading to a potential explosion, which can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Rust or corrosion on the propane tanks
propane smell or leak
hissing sound near the propane tanks
difficulty operating appliances that use propane.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Insufficient Ground Clearance of Trailer Hitch
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The low ground clearance of the trailer hitch can cause damage to the hitch assembly, safety chains, and motorhome, as well as loss of traction, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The trailer hitch hits the pavement when driving into driveways
the safety chains are almost sheared off
the motorhome is lifted up
and the tires almost lose traction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The design of the receiver assembly can cause the hitch assembly to hit the pavement, leading to damage and potential loss of control.
symptoms: The hitch assembly hits the pavement when driving into driveways
the safety chains are almost sheared off
the motorhome is lifted up
and the tires almost lose traction.
